Package pl.polsl.Model

Package with Model class, SortAlgorithm interface and sorting algotihms classes which implements the interface.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Szymon Sochaj
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SortAlgorithm
    SortAlgorithm interface with sort method which is used for implementation of different sort algotihms.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BubbleSort
    Class which implements SortAlgorithm interface, it's used to do the Bubble Sort algorithm.
    InsertionSort
    Class which implements SortAlgorithm interface, it's used to do the Insertion Sort algorithm.
    Model
    Model class used to store the data which are used by the View.
    QuickSort
    Class which implements SortAlgorithm interface, it's used to do the Quick Sort algorithm.
    SelectionSort
    Class which implements SortAlgorithm interface, it's used to do the Selection Sort algorithm.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyFileException
    Exception which is thrown when there is no file, file has no data or the data is incorrect.
